Streaming Aesthetics CLI
========================

Rob Myers <rob@robmyers.org>

twitterstream.py
----------------

A(n oversized) console-based cultural analytics/telemetry application.
Watch running totals of arts-associated word usage on Twitter.

To install dependencies:

sudo pip install TwitterAPI

To configure:

See the instructions in auth_secrets.py.template .

To run:

Resize your console window to be about double usual size, fullscreen works well.
Then type:

python aesthetics_totals.py
